title: Turkish Kitchen
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Pizza, Organic, Mediterranean, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Turkish, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Plenty of plant and vegetable-based items, from hummus, baba ganoush, marinated olives and mixed pickles to rice, falafel, and vegetarian mezze platter. Be sure to ask to omit cheese, yoghurt.
